```python id=bloq
from qualtran.bloqs.basic_gates import ZPowGate
bloq = ZPowGate(exponent=-1/2**(7-1)).controlled()
```
```python id=golden
import numpy as np
# controlled-R7-dagger (control=first, big-endian): diag(1,1,1, exp(-2*pi*i/2**7))
golden = np.diag([1, 1, 1, np.exp(-2j*np.pi/2**7)]).astype(complex)
```
